  • Margin endpoints
Version: Next

Margin endpoints

  

Installation​

Apache Maven

pom.xml
<dependency>
	<groupId>{{groupId}}</groupId>
	<artifactId>{{artifactId}}</artifactId>
	<version>{{version}}</version>
</dependency>

Gradle Groovy DSL

build.gradle
implementation '{{groupId}}:{{artifactId}}:{{version}}'

Client instantiation​

MarginClient client = new MarginClient(key, secret);

Features​

Execute transfer between spot account and cross margin account​

  • Spot to Margin
  • Margin to spot
  • Sync
  • Async (lambda)
  • Async (ApiCallback)
try{
    Transaction res =  client.transfer(new TransferParams(asset, amount, TransferType.MAIN_TO_MARGIN)).sync();
}catch(ApiException e){ 
//...
}
client.transfer(new TransferParams(asset, amount, TransferType.MAIN_TO_MARGIN)).async(response->{
//...
});
client.transfer(new TransferParams(asset, amount, TransferType.MAIN_TO_MARGIN)).async(new ApiCallback<Transaction>() {
    @Override
    public void onResponse(Transaction response) {
        //...
    }

        //...

});
